==============================================================================
INTRODUCTION                                                          *crates*

Crates is a plugin that helps managing crates.io dependencies.
It can display a crate's versions and features and allows you to update,
upgrade, select, enable or disable them.

==============================================================================
USAGE                                                           *crates-usage*

Basic setup.
>
    require('crates').setup()
